data.text:
Lazar Ristovski yesterday he celebrated his 71nd birthday, and his Anica Lazić, a girl 39 years younger shared a joint photo with emotional birthday message for the actor.

– Lazarus (meaning "God helps"). It is believed that a man with this name was sent by God to help the Earth. I know it is so. You are a winner. Benefactor. Our greatest artist. The eternal creator who loves life and therefore life loves you. Protector. An optimist. The patriot. Bold and brave. A great friend. A man with a wide awareness and a good heart. Before I met you I was happy. Now that luck has doubled. You have brightened my life in all fields and every day with you is a blessing. I love you just the way you are. Happy Birthday! - wrote Anica, with a heart emoticon at the end.
